{"tid":2351610,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"見連登好耐冇人開過揭尾故，我開個經典嘅","createTime":"2021-01-03T11:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T14:44:40.000Z","uid":378023,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f40c4f5ac373ce7d8c7add03f7b578367f7a0098","tid":2351610,"uid":378023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:09:48.000Z","msg":"聽過嘅唔好劇透啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n純粹想同未玩過嘅巴絲玩下<br />\n<br />\n從前有三兄弟，<br />\n有一日，大哥死左。<br />\n冇幾耐之後，二哥都死埋。<br />\n點解？<br />\n<br />\n問我問題我只會答是/否/無關<br />\n呢個我覺得都幾恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下大家玩成點"},{"pid":"f13c166b81790659ef68c2e02570b6cc25abde1d","tid":2351610,"uid":335303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"細路黃定藍"},{"pid":"e31a948ccab199317419725c5d0837843f35f31d","tid":2351610,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"呢個玩左咁多年..."},{"pid":"f98709e90727c6fc728b7398d8f58248df5191b0","tid":2351610,"uid":378023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f13c166b81790659ef68c2e02570b6cc25abde1d","tid":2351610,"uid":335303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"細路黃定藍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吓我實支持警犬架喎<br />\n咩問題黎架"},{"pid":"2655499ea47c6e0b0dd66b1fb2f4c8c6bd84f0bc","tid":2351610,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"Keyword<br />\n葬禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d9dc7be228a1e4f14481c6a69124faf690b9a2","tid":2351610,"uid":378023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2655499ea47c6e0b0dd66b1fb2f4c8c6bd84f0bc","tid":2351610,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"Keyword<br />\n葬禮<img sr